description: Frank Fox is all tied up at work and isn't going to get out any time soon. Invoices, product sheets, order forms... aghhh! It's enough to drive him mad. He needs to unwind and loosen up a little, so he decides to go ahead and tie one on... around his dick, that is. Watch as he chokes, binds and eventually squeezes out his workload.Enjoy!
title: Frank Fox
